  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1359320/" class="title-link">遊戲書</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1359320"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/housescheung/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1774804-3.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/housescheung/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">張子房</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2008-04-22"
      class="main-meta">2008-04-22 08:55:21</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1359320_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  不是一本工具書。 看看作者，原來是搞翻譯的高學歷專業人士。 可是他怎麼這麼閒呀？ 我玩過的電玩遊戲他都有在玩，而且比我更清楚！ 讀過的小說他幾乎也讀過，舉列細節一目了然。 與其形容為一本兵器書， 倒不如說是遊戲書， 從另一個角度了解，更添樂趣。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_1359320_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_1359320_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










